<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

    <style>
        body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    }

    /* Main Section Styles */
    .main {
        height: 80vh;
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        color: #fff;
        background-image: url(https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2016/11/22/19/17/buildings-1850129_1280.jpg);
        background-size: cover;
    }

    .main h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        border: 2px solid white;
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .main a.btn {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 767px) {
        .main h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .main a.btn {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
        }
    }
    </style>

    <div class="row mt-3">
        <div class="main">
            <h1>Are You solo traveller?</h1>
            <a class="btn btn-dark btn-col" href="/signup">Join Us</a>
        </div>

        <h3 class="mt-3 heading" >Happy Client</h3>
        <div class="row row-cols-lg-3 mt-3 row-cols-md-2 row-cols-sm-1">
            
        

            <div class="card listing-card col">
                <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2022/02/13/12/05/boy-7011010_1280.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="listing_image" style="height: 20rem;">
                <div class="card-img-overlay">
                    hello
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-text">
                        <b>
                            Carlos M
                        </b><br>
                        I recently stumbled upon the Atithi Devo Bhava website, and it has truly been a game-changer in the way I connect with people. The concept of inviting and hosting random guests in your home intrigued me, and the platform has exceeded my expectations. The user interface is seamless, making the entire process from registration to hosting incredibly easy. It's heartening to see how this platform fosters a sense of community and cultural exchange. Highly recommend it for those seeking enriching experiences!
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card listing-card col">
                <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2017/02/16/23/10/smile-2072907_1280.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="listing_image" style="height: 20rem;">
                <div class="card-img-overlay">
                    hello
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-text">
                        <b>
                            Anna S.
                        </b><br>
                        Atithi Devo Bhava is a unique and wonderful platform that celebrates the spirit of hospitality. I've had the pleasure of hosting diverse individuals from different parts of the world through this website, and it has been a truly enriching experience. The safety measures and communication tools provided by the platform ensured a smooth and secure hosting experience. It's a fantastic way to break down cultural barriers and create lasting connections. I'm grateful for the positive impact it has had on my life.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card listing-card col">
                <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2021/03/14/10/13/girl-6093779_1280.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="listing_image" style="height: 20rem;">
                <div class="card-img-overlay">
                    hello
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="card-text">
                        <b>
                            Lena B
                        </b><br>
                        I can't express enough how amazing my experience has been with Atithi Devo Bhava. The website has successfully created a platform where people from various backgrounds come together under the shared belief that hospitality knows no bounds. The process of inviting and hosting guests is simple and secure, and the community aspect is truly heartwarming. The stories and connections made through this platform are priceless. 
                    
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
           
        </div>

        <div class="col-8 mt-3 ">

            <h3>Contact Us</h3>

            <form class="mb-3" action="/" method="post" novalidate class="needs-validation">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="name" class="form-label">Name</label>
                    <input required name="name" class="form-control" placeholder="enter name" type="text">
                    <div class="invalid-feedback">Please Enter Name</div>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="email" class="form-label">Email</label>
                    <input required name="email" class="form-control" placeholder="enter email" type="email">
                    <div class="invalid-feedback">Please Enter Email</div>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="message" class="form-label">Message</label>
                    <textarea required name="message" class="form-control"></textarea>
                    <div class="invalid-feedback">Your message</div>
                </div>

                <button class="btn btn-dark btn-col">Submit</button>

            </form>
        </div>
    </div>